d Aussie yellow, Titmus led from start to finish.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fingernails\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"Aussie yellow\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"start\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She faced her stiffest challenge from Canadian phenom Summer McIntosh but won comfortably in 3 minutes, 57.49 seconds.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.999999902955101, \"rank\": 9.704508037193928e-08, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her stiffest challenge\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"3 minutes\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"57.49 seconds\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh claimed the silver in 3:58.37.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1714341707497228e-13, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"